column20: I witnessed another version of myself be murdered and came to meet and learn about two versions of myself in other realities who requested my help moving from those to others. In earth space they'd be called dreams. I figured as much until for a month I started being stopped dead in my tracks reexperiencing memories of things I never experienced, and on another occasion literally, audibly heard my son call out "Hey, mom" as he passed behind me while I was at the sink cleaning dishes, only to turn around and find noone there...later discovering he is my son, but in an alternate version. These experiences began in April 2019 and escalated, and were to authentic and legitimate that it set me on a course to try and find out what's happening...leading me on an intriguing journey to simulation theory, alternate realities, dimension hopping, panpsychism, electric universe and a bunch of other topics that have pretty much settled it these are realities. Also, I'm 56 and no longer give a shit what somebody else thinks about my state of mind.
